# w3id.org/alexandria — instance-data namespace of the Alexandria application
# DRAFT for the perma-id/w3id.org PR. Instance IRIs (papers, runs, elements)
# minted by the application resolve here; point at the deployed resolver once
# Alexandria exposes one. Placeholder: the ND-DAC-DOME organization.
Options +FollowSymLinks
RewriteEngine on
RewriteRule ^(.*)$ https://github.com/ND-DAC-DOME [R=303,L]
